Title: Relates to designating a portion of the state highway system as the Assemblyman Pat M. Casale Memorial Bridge
Summary: Relates to designating a portion of the state highway system constituting the bridge crossing over the Hudson River on state route four hundred seventy as the "Assemblyman Pat M. Casale Memorial Bridge".
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the highway law, in relation to designating a portion of the state highway system as the "Assemblyman Pat M. Casale Memorial Bridge"
